Beware - Subscription App - Legal Information: Beware App is here to help to track and manage subscriptions. However Beware App will not ask you to pay using any ways except using payments through Apple App Store. Also, Beware App does not require to submit any users personal data. All data inputted by user is stored only locally on users device and in iCloud in that way so Beware App cannot access users data. Beware App cannot be held responsible for any successfull or unsuccessfull notifiying about users inputted data, such as notifications about future subscriptions. 
